snippet.title: PROPE "PD -prope discoverer-" for iPhone / iPad
snippet.description:
謎に満ちた城から脱出せよ！
iPhoneアプリ史上最高クラスのグラフィックで贈る3D脱出ゲーム、遂に登場！

Escape from a castle full of mysteries!
With the most advanced graphics to date in an iPhone app, get ready for a 3D game of escape!
